22:07.804 --> 22:10.546
♪ Little Shop
Little Shop o' Horrors ♪

22:10.590 --> 22:13.506
♪ Bop sho' bop
Little Shop o' Terror ♪

22:13.549 --> 22:16.422
♪ Watch 'em drop
Little Shop o' Horrors ♪

22:16.465 --> 22:18.728
♪ No-oh-oh-no-oh ♪

22:18.772 --> 22:21.122
♪ Shing-a-ling-shing
Shing-a-ling-thing ♪

22:21.165 --> 22:23.254
♪ What a creepy thing
To be happening ♪

22:23.298 --> 22:25.082
♪ Look out! Look out!
Look out! Look out! Look out! ♪

22:25.126 --> 22:26.823
♪ Shang-a-lang-shang
Lang-shang-a-lang ♪

22:26.867 --> 22:29.435
♪ Feel the Sturm
And Drang in the air ♪

22:29.478 --> 22:30.784
♪ Yeah, yeah, yeah ♪

22:30.827 --> 22:32.568
♪ Sha-la-la-la

22:32.612 --> 22:35.397
♪ Stop right where you are
Don't you move a thing ♪

